"{\"uid\": \"gbnews.com-sport-olympics-tom-daley-olympic-village-complaint-andy-murray-rafael-nadal\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Labour-run council shoots down claim migrant cultures 'do not respect women'  Tom Daley is enjoying life at the Olympic Village so far - but has complained about the food hall being too busy, calling on organisers to 'figure something out'  PA  ByJack Otway,  Published: 01/08/2024  The 30-year-old has won five medals at the Olympics over the years  Tom Daley is enjoying life at the Olympic Village so far - but has complained about the food hall being too busy, calling on organisers to 'figure something out'.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 78, \"end\": 87, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3985253302554925e-43, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 252, \"end\": 257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Otway_National_Park\", \"score\": 0.5949896262674522, \"rank\": 0.6806704162192015, \"text\": \"Otway\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Otway_National_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Otway_National_Park\"}, {\"begin\": 351, \"end\": 360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3985253302554925e-43, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The diving star went into this year's games with four medals to his name and quickly made it five, with the 30-year-old picking up a silver in the men's synchronised 10m platform in Paris.\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 697, \"end\": 702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997355644, \"rank\": 2.6447303761550983e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Daley is an Olympics veteran, having competed for Team GB on the biggest stage of them all ever since 2008.Speaking to GQ Magazine, the diving star dubbed the village 'great'.\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 880, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 824, \"end\": 835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GQ\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"GQ Magazine\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GQ\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GQ\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, he does think the food hall needs sorting out so athletes can eat a little easier.Tom Daley is enjoying life at the Olympic Village so far - but has complained about the food hall being too busy, calling on organisers to 'figure something out'|PA\\\"The village itself is actually quite great,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 1190, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The only thing is the food hall gets busy, but hopefully they will figure that out because as the games go on it's just going to get busier and busier.\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1342, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Daley is surrounded by big names at the games.And he was stunned to see Rafael Nadal, running late for a bus, then 'run into the middle of the bus driveway' to make sure he was on time.JUST IN:Adam Peaty admits to 'offending people' as Team GB face anxious wait on Olympics hero\\\"You know the crazy thing about the Olympic village is you bump into people all the time,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1720, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1415, \"end\": 1427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": 